msgctxt "1348"
msgid "Host Walking to Work"
msgstr "Host de camino al trabajo"

msgctxt "1352"
msgid "Smitten Secretary"
msgstr "Secretaria enamorada"

msgctxt "1356"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "1360"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "1364"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "84_Host Walking to Work"
msgid "You mind if we stop by the convenience store? There's this magazine I want to buy."
msgstr "¿Te importa si pasamos por una tienda? Hay una revista que quiero comprar."

msgctxt "96_Smitten Secretary"
msgid "I don't mind. Hey, if you want, I'll buy it for you!"
msgstr "Está bien. ¡Oye, si quieres te la compro!"

msgctxt "108_Host Walking to Work"
msgid "Aww, you don't have to do that. I mean, you just bought me that watch I'd been wanting, after all."
msgstr "Awww, no te molestes. Quiero decir, me acabas de comprar el reloj que llevo pidiendo hace días."

msgctxt "120_Talk_Yes"
msgid "Oh, I know. Why don't I buy you something for a change. Anything you want－just name it."
msgstr "Ah, sí. ¿Por qué no te compro algo a cambio? Lo que quieras, solo pídelo."

msgctxt "132_Smitten Secretary"
msgid "Really!? You're such a sweetheart, Masaki-kun!"
msgstr "¡¿En serio?! ¡Eres tan dulce, Masaki-kun!"

msgctxt "144_Host Walking to Work"
msgid "Of course! You're a special girl. You deserve to be treated like one."
msgstr "¡Por supuesto! Eres una chica especial. Te mereces que te traten como una."

